# 🧠 Clinical Agentic RAG Pipeline (HW2)

> This project implements an **auditable, agentic RAG pipeline** where every step—from cohort selection to final report—is transparent, reproducible, and grounded in deterministic SQL retrieval.

---

## 🚀 System Overview

This system combines **tool calling + structured retrieval + LLM generation** to produce accurate clinical summaries.

It consists of **three stages**:

1. **Agent 1 (Tool Calling)**
   Identifies a high-risk cohort using a SQL-based function.

2. **RAG Retrieval (Structured Analytics)**
   Builds a JSON payload with cohort-level analytics.

3. **Agent 2 (LLM Generation)**
   Produces a final report using only retrieved data.

---

